location.fullValue: Devonshire II A Plan, Harvest Glen

data.description: This 2-story Craftsman style 3 bedroom/ 2 1/12 bath is only 5 years young and is located in the Triple Creek community of Piedmont.  The exterior features architectural roofing, stone and vinyl siding, an attached 2 car garage, paved driveway. back patio and fenced back yard.  The interior has many great features including Cathedral/vaulted ceilings.  All bedrooms located on upper level.  Master bedroom has full bath with double sink, separate shower and separate tub, and walk-in closet.  Carpeted and vinyl flooring, a spacious kitchen and breakfast room. Natural gas fireplace and grill.  Fireplace has a battery so works when power is out.  CPI Alarm, 6 months transfer.  There is also a community pool. This is a great young home, with great amenities, at a great price.  Schedule your private showing today!
